OL,3,CPresident Connolly to meet Irish
OL,4,Ccommunities during visit to English
OL,5,Ccities
OL,7,FPresident of Ireland Catherine
OL,8,FConnolly will engage with a range of
OL,9,FIrish communities during a visit to
OL,10,FLondon and Leeds.
OL,12,FThe president is making her first
OL,13,Fofficial visit to England since her
OL,14,Finauguration in November, when she
OL,15,Fspoke about her commitment to engaging
OL,16,Fwith the Irish diaspora.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
