PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779066195
OL,3,CPresident Connolly to meet Irish
OL,4,Ccommunities during visit to English
OL,5,Ccities
OL,7,FHer three-day trip will begin on
OL,8,FMonday with a visit to the Irish
OL,9,FCultural Centre in Hammersmith, where
OL,10,Fshe will deliver an address as well as
OL,11,Fmeet with those participating in an
OL,12,FIrish language class.
OL,14,FShe will also view musical and dance
OL,15,Fperformances.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
