CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779066195
OL,3,CPresident Connolly to meet Irish
OL,4,Ccommunities during visit to English
OL,5,Ccities
OL,7,FThe Irish ambassador to Britain Martin
OL,8,FFraser and Deirdre Fraser will host a
OL,9,Freception on Monday evening in honour
OL,10,Fof President Connolly and her husband,
OL,11,FBrian McEnery, at the Irish embassy in
OL,12,FLondon.
OL,14,FThe visit will continue on Tuesday
OL,15,Fwhen the president visits the Chelsea
OL,16,FFlower Show and the London Irish
OL,17,FCentre in Camden.
OL,19,FIt will conclude on Wednesday with
OL,20,Fvisits to Leeds University and the
OL,21,FLeeds Irish Centre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
