PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779066195
OL,3,CPresident Connolly to meet Irish
OL,4,Ccommunities during visit to English
OL,5,Ccities
OL,7,FIn Leeds, President Connolly will be
OL,8,Fbriefed on the work of the Irish
OL,9,FHealth Centre there and will also meet
OL,10,Frepresentatives of other Irish centres
OL,11,Fin the region.
OL,13,FIt is the third official visit the
OL,14,Fpresident has undertaken since
OL,15,Fcommencing her term of office,
OL,16,Ffollowing visits to Northern Ireland
OL,17,Fand Spain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
